+text_pos=155,120,400,left
+text_font=0,0,0,font_cursive
+text=The dig near Perdition Harbor is starting to show promise. We found ruins. Unlike anything else in the area. We'll get a good amount of gold from the relics here. A welcome change for the guys that transferred from the Empyrean's operation in the complex under Lochport.
+requires_status=emp_il_notes_1
